Why backend sends key with every order (even if static)?
1ï¸âƒ£ Environment flexibility (MOST COMMON REAL REASON)

Different environments use different keys:

Environment	Key
Local	rzp_test_xxx
Staging	rzp_test_yyy
Production	rzp_live_zzz

By sending from backend:

